summary: AT 85,263 MILES THE CAR WOULD NOT SHIFT OUT OF 1ST GEAR.  DEALERSHIP ANALYSIS WAS "TRANSMISSION COMING APART INTERNALLY".  NO PARTS AVAILABLE FOR REPAIR.  REQUIRED A NEW TRANSMISSION AT A COST OF $2997.86.  THERE IS NO WAY A TRANSMISSION SHOULD COME APART WITH ONLY 85,000 MILES ON IT.  2ND MAJOR EVENT FOR THIS CAR.
